added.title: The Big Wish
added.description: The bears set off on new adventures with Box being able to transport them anywhere they wish. But what if Box could make their own choices? Would Box even stick around with the bears? If only there were a magical way to find out.

added.title: Polly's New Crew
added.description: The bears reunite with their old friend Polly the Pirate Captain. They soon learn that Polly is under the effect of a pirate curse and need to help them overcome it.

added.title: Snow Place Like Home
added.description: When the Bears realize whatever they build with snow comes to life they decide to build the biggest snow party of all time.

added.title: Fiesta Day
added.description: The Bears party it up with a living piñatas for Fiesta Day. Wanting the festivities to never end, Grizz wishes for it to be Fiesta Day everyday.

added.title: Baba Yaga House
added.description: Squatter Otter tries to win Panda's trust and convince the Bears to live in a mysterious house.

added.title: Life of Pie
added.description: When Izzy, Jude and Owen accidentally bring a pizza to life they do everything they can to help him find a new purpose in life other than being eaten.

added.title: AbaracaDuncan
added.description: When a magic trick goes sideways, Duncan makes a great escape and Harold becomes the target of a Sorcerer Hunt!

added.title: Shock & AWW
added.description: When Courtney gets the old, gross daycare carpet replaced with a new one, the resulting static electricity has unexpected consequences.

added.title: School District 9
added.description: When a career predicting machine tells Owen he has no skills to offer the world, Owen finds a way to prove the machine wrong in the most Owen way possible.

added.title: The A-Bok-Bok-Bokalypse
added.description: When chicken pox sweeps through the school, the kids visit the Chicken Queen to apologize for past misdeeds and hopefully to procure an antidote, before it's too late!

added.title: All Wet
added.description: No one believes Ben when he insists that one of the other patrons waiting in line at the World of Wet Water Park is the nefarious Frightwig disguised as a common girl. So Ben must prove his case while protecting park goers from her master plan: to destroy the park with its own water pressure!

added.title: Villain Time
added.description: Ben must go alien to save the Hoover Dam from disaster, but when tough guy hero Tim Buktu swoops in to help, Ben must figure out if Tim is friend or foe.

added.title: Drive You Crazy
added.description: After the Rust Bucket breaks down at a Mobile Home Park, Ben discovers they've stumbled on to the last leg of the Cali 10 Hundred, an epic, off-road auto race where mad driver Le Grange has returned for revenge against those that disqualified him years ago.

added.title: Tomorrow Today
added.description: When Max drags the kids to see a defunct "House of the Future" built by his childhood idol, Ben discovers Steam Smythe is busy excavating the joint on the search for a powerful device that will allow him to create devastating weapons for his war on progress. Only Max's devotion to his childhood idol and Ben's faith in dreams can save tomorrow... today!

added.title: Story, Bored
added.description: During a book signing at a medieval castle, Ben must stop Hex from getting his hands on a grimoire that can fuse its user with mythical beasts, creating monstrous hybrids!

added.title: Tourist Trap
added.description: While messing with the World's Largest Rubberband Ball at a tourist trap, Ben accidently releases some mischievous electrical creatures.

added.title: Kevin 11
added.description: After a big argument with Max, Ben rebels by going out on his own in the Big Apple and makes friends with Kevin 11, who has plans for the Omnitrix.

added.title: The Alliance
added.description: As Fourarms, Ben works to thwart an armored truck robbery by a tough female gang leader named Joey, who delivers a disturbing message from Vilgax.

added.title: Last Laugh
added.description: Ben's fear of clowns emerges at an unfortunate time when our heroes stumble upon a wicked circus with a psychic vampire clown named Zomobozo.

added.title: Lucky Girl
added.description: Ben battles an evil sorcerer whose power whose emanates from mystic charms, one of which turns Gwen into her own superhero named Lucky Girl.

added.title: Todo Mojado
added.description: Nadie le cree a Ben cuando insiste en que uno de los demás clientes que aguarda en la fila del parque acuático es la malvada Frightwig disfrazada de niña común. Por eso, Ben debe demostrar que dice la verdad mientras protege a los asistentes al parque del plan maestro de la villana: idestruir el parque con su propia presión acuática!

added.title: Hora De Ser Villano
added.description: Ben debe transformarse en alienígena para evitar un desastre en la represa Hoover, pero cuando Tim Buktu, el heroico tipo rudo, se precipita para ayudar, Ben debe descubrir si Tim es su amigo...o su enemigo.

added.title: Conduciendo A La Locura
added.description: Cuando la Chatarra se rompe en un parque de casas rodantes, Ben descubre que se encuentran en la última etapa del Cali 10 Hundred-una carrera de autos épica todo terreno-en la que LaGrange, el piloto demente, ha regresado en busca de venganza contra aquellos que lo descalificaron hace años.

added.title: Manana Es Hoy
added.description: Cuando Max arrastra a los niños a ver una "Casa del futuro" obsoleta construida por su ídolo de la infancia, Ben descubre que Vapor Smythe está ocupado excavando el lugar en busca de un dispositivo poderoso que le permitirá crear armas devastadoras para su guerra en progreso. Solo la devoción de Max por su ídolo de la infancia y la fe de Ben en los sueños puede salvar el mañana...ihoy mismo!

added.title: Lectura, Que Aburrido
added.description: Durante una firma de libros en un castillo medieval, Ben debe impedir que Hex se apodere de un grimorio que puede fusionar a su lector con bestias míticas...iy así crear híbridos monstruosos!

added.title: The Whatsacallit of Treetop Woods/Nat in the Dark!
added.description: Berta is opening an exhibit on the Whatsacallit of Treetop Woods. If only she could get a picture to prove it's real./Gerry and Nat are leading the Treetop Troops on a hike, but Nat finds himself lost in the woods as it gets darker.

added.title: Let's Get Rolling!/A Bit of a Stretch!
added.description: It's MacBarm's croquet tournament and Zee made giant decorations but they're too big to get to the farm./It's the opening day of the skyscraper and the Mechas need to put the sphere on top of the building before the ribbon cutting ceremony.

added.title: Pet T-Rex
added.description: Blippi wonders would a dinosaur have made a good pet?

added.title: Fireflies
added.description: Blippi wonders why do fireflies light up?

added.title: Gravity
added.description: Three, two, one, lift-off! On this mission to the moon, Blippi bounces around with Rocky the Moon Rock. Light as a feather they bound up and float back down, teaching Blippi all about gravity! One small step for Blippi, one giant leap for Blippi.

added.title: Honey
added.description: Blippi and FETCH shrink down and fly inside a very active beehive, where they meet Bijon, the fast-talking, fast-moving Worker Bee. With a talent for rhyming and making honey, Bijon rhymes her way through the sweet explanation of how delicious honey is made. What a very buzzy... erm...busy day!

added.title: Ocean
added.description: Blippi's trusty BlippiMobile safely transports him to a whole new underwater world! He dives into the sea, where he gets an ocean tour from a local resident, Jerry the Jellyfish. They swim through a huge kelp forest, explore the ocean floor and meet interesting underwater creatures along the way!

added.title: Healthy Habits
added.description: A song that highlights what habits everyone should do daily in order to lead a healthy life - brushing their teeth, washing their hands, eating healthy foods and exercising. 'If you want a good day, do everything the healthy way, healthy is the way to be, with your friends at Lellobee'.

added.title: No Monsters Scared of the Dark
added.description: The Baby Pumpkins are scared of the dark as they go to the halloween party!

added.title: Accidents Happen Boo Boo Song
added.description: Ella falls over, but Heidi the Horse teaches her to get right back up again!

added.title: Bath Song
added.description: Ella gets covered in mud so she goes into Mei's farmhouse to have a bath.
